CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season - As Visitors Meet - Dr. Oliver King, a member of the famous Frog Club, is in deep conversation with two pairs of visitors at the formal at Gateway Plaza. Left to right; Dr. King, Dr. Anderson Williams of Kansas City, Mo.; Mrs. Christopher Jeffries and Dr. Jeffries of Altoona. Mrs. Williams is seated while the others stand. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Dr. Oliver King, Dr. Anderson Williams, Mrs. Christopher Jeffries, Mrs. Anderson Williams seated, and Dr. Christopher Jeffries, gathered at banquet table in Gateway Plaza for FROGS formal
